Package: ai-editor-docker
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Vasiliy Zdanovskiy <vasilyvz@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, adduser, python3, curl, ca-certificates
Suggests: man-db
Description: AI Editor MCP server (Docker image + host integration)
 Installs systemd unit, host directories, and pulls the matching Docker Hub image
 on install/upgrade. Config: /etc/ai-editor/ai_editor_container.json,
 data: /var/ai-editor/, logs: /var/log/ai-editor/. Run "ai-editor-info" for status.
